3. cs.BIO (Computational Biology) - The paper deals with the analysis of bio-heat transfer in soft tissue, which is a topic of interest in computational biology. 
4. cs.MS (Mathematical Software) - The paper presents a software implementation of the proposed algorithm for real-time computation of bio-heat transfer, which falls under the scope of mathematical software. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - Although less likely, the paper may also fall under the scope of multimedia as it deals with the analysis of thermal ablative treatments, which may involve the use of imaging and visualization techniques.
